在[[美國|美國]][[德克薩斯州|德克薩斯州]]，'''三一河'''（{{lang-en|Trinity River}}）是一條長約506英里（815公里）的河流。河流發源自德克薩斯州的北部，其流域完全位於州內，面積為17,970平方英里（46,540平方公里）。

== 命名 ==
1687年，法國探險家[[勒內-羅貝爾·卡弗利耶·德·拉薩勒|勒內-羅貝爾·卡弗利耶·德·拉薩勒]]在穿越德克薩斯州時發現了這條河流，並將其命名為「獨木舟河」（{{lang-fr|Riviere des canoës}}）<ref name="History">{{Cite web |url = http://www.trinityra.org/ourhistory |title = Our History |author = Trinity River Authority |language = en |accessdate = 2020-08-05 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://archive.is/20130916213822/http://www.trinityra.org/ourhistory |archivedate = 2013-09-16 }}</ref>。1690年，西班牙探險家{{tsl|en|Alonso de León|阿隆索·德·利昂}}在搜索位於拉瓦卡灣的法國哨站時發現了這條河流，並以神學術語「[[三位一體|三位一體]]」（{{lang-es|Trinidad}}）將其命名為「三一河」（{{lang-es|La Santísima Trinidad}}）<ref name="History"/><ref name="D Magazine@20190520">{{Cite web |url = https://www.dmagazine.com/frontburner/2019/05/is-it-time-to-change-the-name-of-the-trinity-river-back-to-the-arkikosa-river/ |title = Is It Time to Change the Name of the Trinity River Back to the Arkikosa River? |last = Simek |first = Peter |date = 2019-05-20 |publisher = D Magazine |language = en |accessdate = 2020-08-05 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20190605070257/https://www.dmagazine.com/frontburner/2019/05/is-it-time-to-change-the-name-of-the-trinity-river-back-to-the-arkikosa-river/ |archivedate = 2019-06-05 }}</ref>。1691年，另一位西班牙探險家{{tsl|en|Domingo Terán de los Ríos|多明哥·泰蘭·德·洛斯·里奧斯}}亦為這條河流命名<ref name="History"/><ref name="D Magazine@20190520"/>。但由於「三一河」這個名稱更為常用，因此當其他西班牙探險家到達三一河河谷時，當地的原住民則告訴他們這條河名為「三一河」，而後來的探險家亦一致使用這個名字<ref name="History"/><ref name="D Magazine@20190520"/>。

== 流向 ==
三一河有四條分汊，分別是西邊支流、克利爾支流、榆木支流及東邊支流<ref name="Trinity River Basin">{{Cite web |url = https://www.twdb.texas.gov/surfacewater/rivers/river_basins/trinity/index.asp |title = Trinity River Basin |author = Texas Water Development Board |language = en |accessdate = 2020-08-03 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200803102612/https://www.twdb.texas.gov/surfacewater/rivers/river_basins/trinity/index.asp |archivedate = 2020-08-03 }}</ref><ref name="Ulery, Van Metre & Crossfield">{{Cite journal |last = Ulery |first = Randy L. |last2 = Van Metre |first2 = Peter C. |last3 = Crossfield |first3 = Allison S. |title = TRINITY RIVER BASIN, TEXAS |journal = Journal of the American Water Resources Association |year = 1993 |volume = 29 |issue = 4 |pages = 685-711}}</ref>。西邊支流源於[[阿徹縣_(德克薩斯州)|阿徹縣]]，河水先往東南方流經{{tsl|en|Lake Bridgeport (Texas)|布里奇波特湖}}和{{tsl|en|Eagle Mountain Lake|鷹山湖}}，及後往東方流經{{tsl|en|Lake Worth (Texas)|沃斯湖}}和[[沃斯堡|沃斯堡]]<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://tshaonline.org/handbook/online/articles/rnw02 |title = West Fork of the Trinity River |publisher = Texas State Historical Association |language = en |accessdate = 2020-08-03 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200803105204/https://tshaonline.org/handbook/online/articles/rnw02 |archivedate = 2020-08-03 }}</ref>。克利爾支流源於[[韋瑟福德|韋瑟福德]]的北部，河水會先往東南方流經韋瑟福德湖（Lake Weatherford）和{{tsl|en|Benbrook Lake|本布魯克湖}}，及後往東北方流經沃思堡，並在沃思堡市中心附近與西邊支流匯合<ref name="Trinity River">{{Cite web |url = https://tshaonline.org/handbook/online/articles/rnt02 |title = Trinity River |last = Gard |first = Wayne |publisher = Texas State Historical Association |language = en |accessdate = 2020-08-03 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200803110733/https://tshaonline.org/handbook/online/articles/rnt02 |archivedate = 2020-08-03 }}</ref>。榆木支流從[[蓋恩斯維爾_(德克薩斯州)|蓋恩斯維爾]]附近往南流，流經{{tsl|en|Lake Ray Roberts|雷·羅伯茨湖}}和[[登頓_(德克薩斯州)|登頓]]市以東，及後流入{{tsl|en|Lewisville Lake|路易斯維爾湖}}<ref name="Ulery, Van Metre & Crossfield"/>。西邊支流及榆木支流在流經[[達拉斯|達拉斯]]時合流，從而形成三一河<ref name="Trinity River Basin"/><ref name="Ulery, Van Metre & Crossfield"/>。而東邊支流則源於[[麥金尼_(德克薩斯州)|麥金尼]]附近，河水先後流經{{tsl|en|Lavon Lake|拉馮湖}}和{{tsl|en|Lake Ray Hubbard|雷·哈伯德湖}}，並最終在達拉斯的東南方與三一河匯合<ref name="Trinity River Basin"/><ref name="Ulery, Van Metre & Crossfield"/>。與數條分汊匯合後的三一河會往南流，先後流經里奇蘭溪野生動物管理區（Richland Creek Wildlife Management Area）<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://tpwd.texas.gov/huntwild/hunt/wma/find_a_wma/list/?id=23 |title = Richland Creek (WMA) |author = Texas Parks and Wildlife Department |language = en |accessdate = 2020-08-04 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200608055347/https://tpwd.texas.gov/huntwild/hunt/wma/find_a_wma/list/?id=23 |archivedate = 2020-06-08 }}</ref>、大湖底野生動物管理區（Big Lake Bottom Wildlife Management Area）<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://tpwd.texas.gov/huntwild/hunt/wma/find_a_wma/list/?id=1 |title = Big Lake Bottom WMA |author = Texas Parks and Wildlife Department |language = en |accessdate = 2020-08-04 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200309134128/https://tpwd.texas.gov/huntwild/hunt/wma/find_a_wma/list/?id=1 |archivedate = 2020-03-09 }}</ref>及[[三一縣_(德克薩斯州)|三一縣]]附近，並流入位於[[山姆·休斯敦國家森林|山姆·休斯敦國家森林]]東北面的{{tsl|en|Lake Livingston|利文斯頓湖}}<ref name="Ulery, Van Metre & Crossfield"/><ref name="Trinity River"/>。離開利文斯頓湖，三一河會繼續往南流，最終在[[錢伯斯縣_(得克薩斯州)|錢伯斯縣]]流入位於{{tsl|en|Galveston Bay|加爾維斯頓灣}}北部的{{tsl|en|Trinity Bay (Texas)|三一灣}}<ref name="Ulery, Van Metre & Crossfield"/><ref name="Trinity River"/>。

== 公共工程 ==
[[File:Trinity_River_view1.jpg|left]]

在1890年代，一群商人為了促進三一河的河道交通，因而組建了三一河航行公司（Trinity River Navigation Company）<ref name="Slate@20140925">{{Cite web |url = http://www.slate.com/blogs/the_eye/2014/09/25/_99_invisible_roman_mars_on_the_attempted_creation_of_the_port_of_dallas.html |title = How Landlocked Dallas Once Tried to Become a Port City |last = Barton |first = Julia |date = 2014-09-25 |publisher = Slate |language = en |accessdate = 2020-08-04 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200130074012/http://www.slate.com/blogs/the_eye/2014/09/25/_99_invisible_roman_mars_on_the_attempted_creation_of_the_port_of_dallas.html |archivedate = 2020-01-30 }}</ref>。這間公司後來建造了一艘挖泥船來進行[[疏浚|疏浚]]工程，並成功使河流通航<ref name="Dallas Morning News@20190620">{{Cite web |url = https://www.dallasnews.com/news/curious-texas/2019/06/20/why-doesnt-dallas-use-the-trinity-river-as-a-port-curious-texas-investigates/ |title = Why doesn’t Dallas use the Trinity River as a port? Curious Texas investigates |last = Limón |first = Elvia |date = 2019-06-20 |publisher = The Dallas Morning News |language = en |accessdate = 2020-08-04 |archive-date = 2020-08-04 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200804125600/https://www.dallasnews.com/news/curious-texas/2019/06/20/why-doesnt-dallas-use-the-trinity-river-as-a-port-curious-texas-investigates/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>。達拉斯市政府其後說服國會，促使聯邦政府調查三一河並找出哪裡可以興建閘壩，以提升河流的通航能力<ref name="Dallas Morning News@20190620"/>。1909年，[[美國陸軍工兵部隊|美國陸軍工兵部隊]]在達拉斯市{{convert|13|mi|km}}外的麥科馬斯崖（McCommas Bluff）附近建造了第1座閘壩<ref name="Slate@20140925"/><ref name="Mitchell@1990">{{Cite journal |last = Mitchell |first = David |url = https://scholarworks.sfasu.edu/cgi/viewcontent.cgi?article=2040&context=ethj |title = The Trinity River Project, 1852-1922 |journal = East Texas Historical Jouranl |year = 1990 |volume = 28 |issue = 2 |pages = 39-45 |access-date = 2020-08-05 |archive-date = 2020-07-09 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200709152712/https://scholarworks.sfasu.edu/cgi/viewcontent.cgi?article=2040&context=ethj |dead-url = no }}</ref>。最初聯邦政府的計劃是從達拉斯至三一灣興建37座閘壩，而國會亦每年撥款予這個項目，但最終因美國參與[[第一次世界大戰|第一次世界大戰]]而停止<ref name="Mitchell@1990"/>{{sfn|United States War Department|1919|p=1136}}。1921年，這個航行項目因成本太高而被放棄<ref name="Trinity River Navigation Projects">{{Cite web |url = https://tshaonline.org/handbook/online/articles/ett01 |title = Trinity River Navigation Projects |last = Gard |first = Wayne |publisher = Texas State Historical Association |language = en |accessdate = 2020-08-04 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200729021635/https://tshaonline.org/handbook/online/articles/ett01 |archivedate = 2020-07-29 }}</ref>。最終，聯邦政府在三一河所興建的只有1號、2號、4號、6號、7號、20號及25號閘壩<ref name="Mitchell@1990"/>{{sfn|United States War Department|1919|p=1136}}。

1998年，時任達拉斯市市長的[[罗恩·柯克|罗恩·柯克]]提出了一項旨在修整流經達拉斯的河流的計劃——「{{tsl|en|Trinity River Project|三一河計劃}}」<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.dmagazine.com/publications/d-magazine/2010/january/birth-of-the-trinity-river-corrider-project/ |title = Birth of the Trinity River Corrider Project |last = Bartlett |first = Steve |date = 2010 |publisher = D Magazine |language = en |accessdate = 2020-08-04 |archive-date = 2020-08-04 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200804171859/https://www.dmagazine.com/publications/d-magazine/2010/january/birth-of-the-trinity-river-corrider-project/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>。選民們其後投票通過了一項債券計劃，以資助河流清理、公園設施的建設、野生動植物棲息地、防洪堤等防洪設備以及相關的道路建設<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.texasobserver.org/3060-if-they-build-it-dallas-long-and-winding-trinity-river-corridor-project/ |title = If They Build It… Dallas' long and winding Trinity River Corridor Project |last = Dille |first = Ian |date = 2009-05-29 |publisher = D Magazine |language = en |accessdate = 2020-08-04 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150921071012/https://www.texasobserver.org/3060-if-they-build-it-dallas-long-and-winding-trinity-river-corridor-project/ |archivedate = 2015-09-21 }}</ref>。2004年，三一信託基金會成立，以提高公眾意識及獲得私人資金來支持三一河計劃，包括{{tsl|en|Margaret Hunt Hill Bridge|瑪格麗特·亨特·希爾大橋}}、{{tsl|en|Margaret McDermott Bridge|瑪格麗特·麥克德莫特大橋}}、{{tsl|en|Ronald Kirk Bridge|羅恩·柯克大橋}}及其他設施<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://thetrinitytrust.org/the-trinity-trust/ |title = About Us |author = Trinity Park Conservancy |language = en |accessdate = 2020-08-04 |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20190915035353/http://thetrinitytrust.org/the-trinity-trust/ |archivedate = 2019-09-15 }}</ref>。

== 洪水及防洪措施 ==
三一河在1844年、1866年、1871年及1890年都曾經發生過洪災，但唯獨在1908年春季發生的洪災推動了政府對三一河的治理<ref name="D Magazine@20170311">{{Cite web |url = https://www.dmagazine.com/publications/d-magazine/2017/march/wild-dallas-trinity-river-guide-dallas/taming-the-trinity/ |title = Taming the Trinity |last = Simek |first = Peter |date = 2017-03-11 |publisher = D Magazine |language = en |accessdate = 2020-08-05 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170311013052/https://www.dmagazine.com/publications/d-magazine/2017/march/wild-dallas-trinity-river-guide-dallas/taming-the-trinity/ |archivedate = 2017-03-11 }}</ref>。1908年5月下旬，德克薩斯州廣泛地區受大雨影響，而[[阿比林_(得克萨斯州)|阿比林]]市更在5月22日至23日這24小時內錄得{{convert|6.78|inch|mm}}的降雨量{{sfn|Burnett|2008|p=300}}。其後洪災發生，淹沒了三一河流域及努埃塞斯河流域{{sfn|Burnett|2008|p=300}}。而在達拉斯市，三一河的水位上升至{{convert|52.6|ft|m}}並估計約{{convert|2|mi|km}}寬{{sfn|Burnett|2008|p=300}}。這次洪災導致5人死亡，超過4,000名居民無家可歸，財產損失估計為250萬美元<ref name="Dallas Morning News@20190620"/><ref name="D Magazine@20170311"/>。而達拉斯市的大部份基礎設施亦因這次洪災而受損，包括供水廠和供電廠被淹沒，橋樑及鐵路設施遭到損壞，所有的電話和電報服務中斷<ref name="Dallas Morning News@20190620"/><ref name="D Magazine@20170311"/>。此外，成千上萬的牲畜被洪水淹死，有部份的牲畜更被洪水沖至樹頂，而隨著洪水的消退，屍體腐爛的惡臭更籠罩著整個城市<ref name="D Magazine@20170311"/>{{sfn|Payne|1982|pp=119-155}}。

